# 📁 8. Folder Structure (Best Practice)

Create your own folder:

```
yourname/
   file-transfer-service/
      input/
      archive/
      output/
```

## Purpose

* `input` → source files
* `archive` → processed files
* `output` → final output

⚠️ Never modify others’ folders

